import React from 'react'; import { FaGithub, FaLinkedin, FaTwitter } from 'react-icons/fa'; import './About.css'; const teamMembers = [ { name: 'John Doe', role: 'Founder & CEO', image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80', bio: 'Passionate about books and technology. Founded BookStore to make reading accessible to everyone.', social: { github: 'https://github.com/johndoe', linkedin: 'https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe', twitter: 'https://twitter.com/johndoe' } }, { name: 'Jane Smith', role: 'Head of Operations', image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80', bio: 'Book enthusiast with 10+ years of experience in e-commerce and customer service.', social: { github: 'https://github.com/janesmith', linkedin: 'https://linkedin.com/in/janesmith', twitter: 'https://twitter.com/janesmith' } }, { name: 'Mike Johnson', role: 'Lead Developer', image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519244703995-f4e0f30006d5?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80', bio: 'Full-stack developer with a passion for creating seamless user experiences.', social: { github: 'https://github.com/mikejohnson', linkedin: 'https://linkedin.com/in/mikejohnson', twitter: 'https://twitter.com/mikejohnson' } } ]; const About = () => { return (

About BookStore

Your Gateway to Literary Adventures

Our Mission

At BookStore, we believe that books have the power to transform lives. Our mission is to make quality literature accessible to everyone, fostering a community of readers and lifelong learners.

Meet Our Team

{teamMembers.map((member) => (

{member.name}

{member.role}

{member.bio}

))}

Our Values

Quality

We curate only the best books for our readers.

Accessibility

Making books available to everyone, everywhere.

Community

Building a vibrant community of book lovers.

); }; export default About;
